# Setting up Auth.js v5 and Okta

Primary reference: `skills/setting-up-nextauth-okta/SKILL.md`

Use this rule for:

- dev Okta app creation
- Auth.js v5 (`next-auth@5.x` + `@auth/prisma-adapter`) wiring
- the App Router exception for `app/api/auth/[...nextauth]/route.ts`
- SessionProvider setup
- `auth()`-protected API routes
- the `auth` health check registered in `/api/health`
- `.env.example` and `.env.local` conventions (`AUTH_SECRET`, `AUTH_URL`, `AUTH_TRUST_HOST`, `OKTA_*`)
